Puppet module: yum

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages yum software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include yum              # Install and run yum with standard configurations.
include yum::disable     # Disable yum service.
include yum::disableboot # Disable yum service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include yum::absent      # Remove yum package.

DEPENDENCIES:
